@StadiumAnalytics.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5142

### Ingest a gate sensor event (POST required)
POST {{StadiumAnalytics.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gate": "Gate A",
  "timestamp": "2023-04-01T08:00:00Z",
  "numberOfPeople": 10,
  "type": "enter"
}

### Analytics summary
GET {{StadiumAnalytics.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/analytics/summary

###
